{"tid":878312,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"袁偉豪奇怪冇得雙提名 譚俊彥拉票一舊雲","createTime":"2018-10-27T04:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T13:48:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1cdda7b5df456fda0e7a510eef1a1b4c625724c2","tid":878312,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"袁偉豪亦隨隊出發到星馬拉票，他憑《棟仁的時光》入圍，將力敵《再創世紀》的郭晉安、《兄弟》王浩信、《天命》陳展鵬，對於未能憑《三個女人一個「因」》入圍，袁偉豪直認感可惜：「其實我有啲奇怪呢套劇冇提名視帝，我覺得兩劇都可以被提名，因為兩個演出都唔同，《三個》色彩多啲、搞笑同幽默啲又辛苦啲，但就以女性為主導，《棟仁》就淡然啲，睇吓觀眾鍾意咩劇種。（睇好自己攞獎？）有份角逐都希望有收穫，邊度嘅獎都一樣，三個地方即係有三分一機會攞。」他還揚言今次到星馬最想幫拍檔黃智雯拉票，因為當日她拍得很辛苦，睇好對方奪視后。<br />\n<br />\n而同行的譚俊彥憑《天命》入圍爭視帝，首度到當地拉票的他卻搞笑「一舊雲」：「唔知去到要做乜，跟大隊，當秋季旅行，去玩同食。」對於以往在馬來西亞舉行的《TVB馬來西亞星光薈萃頒獎禮》及新加坡舉行的《星和無綫電視大獎》今年將取消，改於無綫台慶當日頒發視帝視后，他不感可惜：「因為之前冇經歷過呢兩個頒獎禮，有份參與角逐已經好開心，我哋拍套劇最想係有人睇，希望大家支持。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a.fJQ_RmxxHTzdtosh7bNg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/68e2325e3017f32ab16a16121d978f78\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fa.fJQ_RmxxHTzdtosh7bNg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F68e2325e3017f32ab16a16121d978f78&h=4b2fc723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5yyEOsrM0pLxxvPyAsGqUA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/f7fa514aa9f05afb6b0eab85d7b4ee1b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5yyEOsrM0pLxxvPyAsGqUA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Ff7fa514aa9f05afb6b0eab85d7b4ee1b&h=f255ab18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f5def79d774df2d43ad434d8873d88cda97506c","tid":878312,"uid":20653,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"repl